              </div>
              <div class="media-grid">
                <figure><img src="project_showcase_component/assets/orbit-detail-1.svg" alt="Placeholder detail visual showing Project Orbit content structure" /><figcaption>Content structure</figcaption></figure>
                <figure><img src="project_showcase_component/assets/orbit-detail-2.svg" alt="Placeholder detail visual showing Project Orbit page layout" /><figcaption>Page layout</figcaption></figure>
              </div>
              <div class="video-block">
                <video controls preload="metadata" poster="project_showcase_component/assets/orbit-poster.svg"><source src="project_showcase_component/assets/placeholder-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />Your browser does not support the video element.</video>
                <p>Replace the source with a real project demo video.</p>
              </div>
              <section class="project-outcome"><h3>Outcome</h3><p>Document the project’s final impact.</p></section>
